Welcome to the FORE Learning Hub!

FORE: Fundamentals of Robotics Education is an interactive learning website for those of a high school to undergraduate level with an interest in learning how to program robotics!
I am a Student with a class FORE is an environment that you may learn under the supervision of an instructor who has made a class of their own. Sign up for the class and complete assignments, quizzes, and projects assigned by your teacher! I am an independent learner FORE is also designed for those who are simply interested in trying robotics out and do not have access to hardware. Follow our pre-determined learning path and start programming robotics today!
